{"tid":1964696,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Zoom股東控高層隱瞞","createTime":"2020-04-09T04:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T00:14:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d2009db3c1380319119e5e477198f5fadd49a515","tid":1964696,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T04:15:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200409/KQKGB6WGEOVY4ABXNTEB3RYSFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200409%2FKQKGB6WGEOVY4ABXNTEB3RYSFI%2F&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbvBNkMLqpq56k8mIdjvCyJE%3D&h=d65ab3e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200409%2FKQKGB6WGEOVY4ABXNTEB3RYSFI%2F&h=9b67c2d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200409/KQKGB6WGEOVY4ABXNTEB3RYSFI/</a><br />\n<br />\nZoom股東控高層隱瞞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200409/large/1586363324_e36d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200409%2Flarge%2F1586363324_e36d.jpg&h=66667e85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】根據彭博報道，視像會議軟件Zoom股東Michael Drieu在三藩市提出集體訴訟，指控公司及高層隱瞞應用程式的保安漏洞，包括輕易受黑客攻擊及容許一些未經授權的個人資料予如facebook的第三方等，令股東以為Zoom可受惠於武漢肺炎令股價上升。<br />\n<br />\n在公佈消息後，Zoom的股價在盤前受壓，報110.5元，較昨日美股收市價跌2.85%，市值蒸發8.25億美元（約64億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n在上周被曝保安漏洞前，包括創辦人袁征在內的管理層在第一季已通過出售股份，套現近超過8,800萬美元（約6.82億港元），而在被曝私隱漏洞後，Zoom已經暫停功能更新完善安全性。<br />\n<br />\n包括台灣政府及Tesla大股東馬斯克旗下的探索公司SpaceX在內公司已停用Zoom。袁征亦在後來向用戶致歉，並承諾會盡快解決漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠料損失61億<br />\n<br />\n根據美國證券交易委員會的資料，現時李嘉誠旗下公司合計持有1,455.8萬股，佔股本5.21%，以股價最高位164.94美元計算，損失金額約7.93億美元（約61.42億港元）。"},{"pid":"d8e47726888a0ca388beb4381466e899421f308d","tid":1964696,"uid":54126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T04:16:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那野"},{"pid":"2913fdfc719306f144d55e86